Class ProductData

  • java.lang.Object
    • xml.Requirement
      • xml.ProductData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProductData, IRequirement

    public class ProductData
extends Requirement
implements IProductData
    Class to hold the ProductData of the requirement analysis. This class provides JAXB support and can be accessed via the IProductData Interface. Getter and Setter must be provided to be JAXB conform. It is implemented in the CustomXMLFormat.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    3852430
    See Also:
    IProductData, CustomXMLFormat
